{"tid":1328239,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）連仔快入","createTime":"2019-07-18T00:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:07:08.000Z","uid":73392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d29834878f4c72e92f132f26e6f6c1cf838a793","tid":1328239,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:42:44.000Z","msg":"連登一去到凌晨，根本就唔係連登，而係五毛登，成班135毛，瘋狂開post，瘋狂推垃圾post，大量刷正負評，一起身個個熱門post都係135毛開嘅，根本凌晨時份嘅連登，唔係一個討論區，而係一班收左錢嘅人，9叫嘅洗版區，嚴重違反左討論區應有嘅討論功能<br />\n<br />\n故此強烈建議，應限制凌晨時份開post，推post嘅次數<br />\n<br />\n或者該時段開嘅post，同推嘅post，要有200留言加2000正負評數，才可以上熱門<br />\n<br />\n又或者設立，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">凌晨熱門台</span>，將所有凌晨至上熱門嘅post歸類為凌晨熱門，令大眾係區分資訊時，多一個參考<br />\n<br />\n求連仔接納建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845c00e42c3bc40cb0bf4957911a712807f75737","tid":1328239,"uid":262618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f3d00371e4926ce70404bc1cbb76eff069c1d57","tid":1328239,"uid":239842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:43:46.000Z","msg":"隔夜熱門呢招絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07055fdeffef94766346acafb995a6324d739ac3","tid":1328239,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"a2ba80c5871f90fb071a5ee662f09567d5cf16a3","tid":1328239,"uid":73392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f3d00371e4926ce70404bc1cbb76eff069c1d57","tid":1328239,"uid":239842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:43:46.000Z","msg":"隔夜熱門呢招絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-